    <p><anchor n="X.88.1646.0184c16"/><lb ed="X" n="0184c16"/><persName key="A014804">安元</persName><placeName key="PL000000048413">安息國</placeName>人也。志性貞白。為優婆塞。嚴秉法戒。博<lb ed="X" n="0184c17"/>通群經。<date key="j17884261790419" to-iso="0189-11-24" from-iso="0184-06-10">漢靈帝末</date>游宦<placeName key="PL000000023521">洛陽</placeName>。官騎都尉。常與沙門講<lb ed="X" n="0184c18"/>論道義。時僧<persName key="A001912">佛調</persName>方譯法鏡經。<persName key="A014804">元</persName>口譯梵文。<persName key="A001912">佛調</persName>筆<lb ed="X" n="0184c19"/>受。詞旨兩得。見述後代(出三藏記集)。</p>     
    
